items.title: Retailers post early holiday results — and Wall Street isn’t impressed
items.description: Lululemon, Abercrombie & Fitch and American Eagle all hiked their holiday guidance, but Abercrombie's growth is slowing.

items.title: Delta outlook tops estimates as CEO expects 2025 to be airline's 'best financial year in our history'
items.description: Delta's CEO said strong travel demand is driving revenue higher.

items.title: Walgreens shares soar 27% on big earnings beat, as drugstore chain cuts costs
items.description: Walgreens maintained its fiscal 2025 adjusted earnings guidance, but did not include a sales outlook in its release.

items.title: Corona brewer gets slammed post-earnings, and we question whether to keep the stock
items.description: This was not the quarter we were looking for — and unfortunately, we see little reason to defend Constellation brands.

items.title: World's biggest chipmaker TSMC posts record 2024 revenue as AI boost continues
items.description: TSMC manufacturers semiconductors for some of the world's biggest companies from Apple to Nvidia.
